# 🔥 BUILD PROMPT — Pure Pay-Per-Use Monetization (NO FREE TIER)

## 🎯 Goal

**100% pay-per-use pricing engine** - every action costs credits upfront. No free tiers, no subscriptions, pure consumption billing.

### ✅ Features

* Credit-only access (buy packs to use)  
* Real-time predicted costs per action  
* Hard spend caps per user/org  
* Self-serve credit packs ($10-500)  
* Usage dashboards with cost forecasts  
* Graceful service suspension at 0 credits  

### ⚙ Functions

* `buyCredits(packSize: 1k|5k|10k|50k|100k)` → Stripe session  
* `predictActionCost(action: string, context: any)` → `{base: number, total: number}`  
* `deductCredits(userId: string, amount: number)` → `{success: boolean, remaining: number}`  
* `getUsageForecast(userId: string)` → `{today: number, monthly: number, cap: number}`  
* `setSpendLimit(userId: string, limit: number)` → hard cap enforcement  

### 🧩 Components

* `credit-wallet.tsx`  
* `cost-predictor.tsx`  
* `buy-credits-modal.tsx`  
* `usage-forecast.tsx`  
* `spend-limit-setter.tsx`  

### 🔌 Integrations

* Stripe (Checkout + Customer Portal + Usage Records)  
* Neon (credit balances table)  
* Drizzle (credit transactions)  

### 📦 Dependencies

* stripe  
* drizzle-orm  
* @neondatabase/serverless  
* lucide-react  
* @radix-ui/react-dialog  

### 🤖 AI Functions

* **Cost estimator**: Predict credits needed before action starts  
* **Budget advisor**: "At current rate, you'll need $47 more credits this month"  
* **Usage optimizer**: "Switch to cheaper model to save 30% on next run"  

